    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i just feel like 5mg is a lot for someone as active as me now. i've been reading some stuff online and it seems like people on lower doses stay stable for years without issues. if i just taper it down slowly myself, like to 2mg, wouldn't that be a safer way to see how my body reacts? i'm just worried about the side effects of being on such a high dose long term.",
